#

Creamy Brussels Sprouts Gratin

45 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

AmericanFrench

Course:

Side DishVegetable Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodVegetable Dish

Description

A rich and creamy dish featuring tender Brussels sprouts baked in a cheesy sauce, topped with a crispy breadcrumb layer.

Ingredients

  • brussels sprouts: 1 lb
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • shredded gruyère cheese: 1 cup
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup
  • breadcrumbs: 1/2 cup
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • butter: 2 tbsp
